name: Pillow hexagon 50x50cm
description:
Pillow.
Size: 50 x 50 cm., 19,7 x 19,7 inches.

"Two sides to every hexagonpillow."

Front: stroke and colors.
Bag: Grey and simple.

This pillow is digital printed on a 100% eco-friendly cotton – a woven ½ Panama.
The hexagonprint is a limited edition print. It will only be available in a shorter period of time - so act fast...

Wash at 30 degrees delicate wash/"skånevask" - inside out
Stretch carefully in wet state. Can be ironed.
Do not tumble dry.

name: Pillow umbrella black 50x50cm
description:
Pillow.
Size: 50 x 50 cm., 19,7 x 19,7 inches.

LykkeBang fabrics are printed on 100% eco-friendly cotton – a woven ½ Panama.
The fabric is coated with a anti-dirtsurface so it can resist dirt better.
All fabrics are hand-printed and all the colors, environmentally friendly, are mixed by LykkeBang.
Prints, patterns and colors may not always be 100% identical – pure unica products.

Wash at 40 to 60 degrees. Stretch carefully in wet state. Can be ironed, but always be careful with the fabric.
Tumble drying is not recommended.
